{"ja460:0.1":"Jataka ","ja460:0.2":"Ekadasakanipata ","ja460:0.3":"Matuposakavagga ","ja460:0.4":"6. Yudhancayajataka ","ja460:1.1":"“Mittamaccaparibyulham, ","ja460:1.2":"aham vande rathesabham; ","ja460:1.3":"Pabbajissamaham raja, ","ja460:1.4":"tam devo anumannatu”. ","ja460:2.1":"“Sace te unam kamehi, ","ja460:2.2":"aham paripurayami te; ","ja460:2.3":"Yo tam himsati varemi, ","ja460:2.4":"ma pabbaja yudhancaya”. ","ja460:3.1":"“Na matthi unam kamehi, ","ja460:3.2":"himsita me na vijjati; ","ja460:3.3":"Dipanca katumicchami, ","ja460:3.4":"yam jara nabhikirati”. ","ja460:4.1":"“Putto va pitaram yace, ","ja460:4.2":"pita va puttamorasam; ","ja460:4.3":"Negamo tam yace tata, ","ja460:4.4":"ma pabbaja yudhancaya”. ","ja460:5.1":"“Ma mam deva nivarehi, ","ja460:5.2":"pabbajantam rathesabha; ","ja460:5.3":"Maham kamehi sammatto, ","ja460:5.4":"jaraya vasamanvagu”. ","ja460:6.1":"“Aham tam tata yacami, ","ja460:6.2":"aham putta nivaraye; ","ja460:6.3":"Ciram tam datthumicchami, ","ja460:6.4":"ma pabbaja yudhancaya”. ","ja460:7.1":"“Ussavova tinaggamhi, ","ja460:7.2":"suriyuggamanam pati; ","ja460:7.3":"Evamayu manussanam, ","ja460:7.4":"ma mam amma nivaraya”. ","ja460:8.1":"“Taramano imam yanam, ","ja460:8.2":"aropetu rathesabha; ","ja460:8.3":"Ma me mata tarantassa, ","ja460:8.4":"antarayakara ahu”. ","ja460:9.1":"“Abhidhavatha bhaddante, ","ja460:9.2":"sunnam hessati rammakam; ","ja460:9.3":"Yudhancayo anunnato, ","ja460:9.4":"sabbadattena rajina. ","ja460:10.1":"Yohu settho sahassassa, ","ja460:10.2":"yuva kancanasannibho; ","ja460:10.3":"Soyam kumaro pabbajito, ","ja460:10.4":"kasayavasano bali”. ","ja460:11.1":"“Ubho kumara pabbajita, ","ja460:11.2":"yudhancayo yudhitthilo; ","ja460:11.3":"Pahaya matapitaro, ","ja460:11.4":"sangam chetvana maccuno”ti. ","ja460:12.1":"Yudhancayajatakam chattham. "}